    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document creates a new IANA registry for tracking cost modes supported by the Application-Layer Traffic Optimization (ALTO) Protocol. Also, this document relaxes a constraint that was imposed by the ALTO specification on allowed cost mode values.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document updates RFC 7285.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
